闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-7d1f88736f9d393dbda64760b7ed5468_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/578281704"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iq9Pq98bAgaNAEAMaCDkwNzg4NTE1IPvE/p0GMAM4gQFAEXIJNTc4MjgxNzA0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "18_1675285674.8701549", "card_id": "Q_581700919", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "外媒称中国今天起对自韩赴华旅客进行核酸检测，外交部称「对个别国家不得不按照对等原则回应」，如何解读？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "外交部发言人毛宁 1 日主持例行记者会。有外媒记者提问称，中国政府从今天起对自韩国赴华的旅客进行核酸检测。外交部能否提供更多信息？ 毛宁表示，我们愿意同各国一道尽可能地便利中外人员往来，但是对于个别国家执意采取针对中国公民的歧视性措施，我们不得不按照对等的原则回应。（环球时报）中国从今天起对自韩国赴华旅客进行核酸检测？外交部回应"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "90 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/581700919"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iq9Pq98bAgaNAEAMaCDkxNTQ4MjYxIKSy6J4GMAQ4UUAScgk1ODE3MDA5MTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "19_1675285674.8709197", "card_id": "Q_581731408", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价最高搭载 4090 的机械师曙光 16 Pro？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4904388d9f0e84e932d19bf23de5f572_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "83 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/581731408"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Iq9Pq98bAgaNAEAMaCDkxNTU1MDQ0IKWq6Z4GMAA4OUATcgk1ODE3MzE0MDh4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id"